    {
      "id": "042b3071-5ed6-438c-a55e-62d9231549d9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "By integrating a more robust model of student relationships, the feature space now includes dimensions that were not observable before, which results into the creation of better and more accurate predictive models. Validation of the new model against traditional classifiers AND Graph neural networks on 4 real-world datasets demonstrates the superiority of the designed approach. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
